      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEKTRA BILLS (1) turned in a better effort at Geelong last start, finishing second behind She Rebel (22.64) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Sure to be about the mark. ASTON WARRIOR (2) has missed the frame at his last couple of starts but just a few runs back broke the clock when winning over 390m at this track, taking a Grade 4/5 in an outstanding 22.02. Top win three back and can measure up again. PAW PALMER (6) was never in contention last time after losing his position early at Geelong, but prior to that won easily by 4.5 lengths at Geelong (22.35) beating Paw Judd in a Grade 5 on March 6. Cannot be underestimated. COLLECTIVE KAOS (8) placed last time at this track and distance - worth some thought.",
